modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds the steel [ammo](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-ammo/) from A17 for players who enjoyed that option.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/KhaineGB/khaines-modlets-a19/-/archive/master/khaines-modlets-a19-master.zip?path=KHA19-SteelAmmo)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19558-khaines-a19-modlets-bigger-backpacks-backpack-buttons-hp-bars-etc/).
